{"tid":937969,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想認真學英文 比啲意見得唔得？","createTime":"2018-12-12T02:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T18:01:13.000Z","uid":37726,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f70f6852b22b47c31ba3fe49c8b2c73ec3bed4db","tid":937969,"uid":37726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"講返少少依家既程度<br />\n水平可能連小學都不如<br />\n記生字可能好啲 但都係差<br />\nGrammar 就唔洗講 <br />\n如果有個外國人問我嘢 <br />\n就只可以將識既生字同最基本既Grammar重組<br />\n最後可能對方都聽唔明<br />\n<br />\n依家我就通常見到唔識既生字<br />\n即刻記低落手機 <br />\n再搵返中文意思同搵多個相近既英文字<br />\n但係咁樣對我嚟講 幫助真係唔大<br />\n<br />\n有諗過讀夜校進修<br />\n或者去書局買返由小學開始既練習慢慢做<br />\n咁樣又有冇幫助？<br />\n<br />\n如果想打返好基礎<br />\n英文溝通同睇得明<br />\n有冇咩方法？辛苦少少都唔緊要<br />\n又或者分享下 你地學英文有咩習慣"},{"pid":"431835e75e16cc8bfc903c0691e8b63f495e97f7","tid":937969,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":45,"score":-38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be8d3057e6322073f74100457bde5afb62692eb9","tid":937969,"uid":37726,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"431835e75e16cc8bfc903c0691e8b63f495e97f7","tid":937969,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":45,"score":-38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"又好 不過學咗英文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca7e5c5af7d91ac3d5477b7cc143b228a63511b","tid":937969,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"中學畢業未"},{"pid":"30ff361bd9cab136baf738aaefbedc4db7d013c8","tid":937969,"uid":37726,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"4ca7e5c5af7d91ac3d5477b7cc143b228a63511b","tid":937969,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"中學畢業未"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:32:00.000Z","msg":"唔記得講<br />\n中學畢咗<br />\n但我dse 得1"},{"pid":"f064567001fc9688034e8ee95eaec61b540bdcba","tid":937969,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dis